<p style="text-align: justify;"><img src="/img/article/body/127a8a66034572732efe0a76eca335d5b5f146b2.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dii fr-fil" style="width: 300px;">1999 &oacute;ta tart &eacute;v&eacute;rt&eacute;kelő besz&eacute;deket Orb&aacute;n Viktor - minisztereln&ouml;kk&eacute;nt vagy ellenz&eacute;ki vezetők&eacute;nt -, a mostani, <a href="https://dex.hu/x.php?id=index_belfold_cikklink&url=https%3A%2F%2Findex.hu%2Fbelfold%2F2019%2F02%2F10%2Ftuntetesekkel_keszulnek_orban_viktor_evertekelojere%2F" target="_self">21. &eacute;v&eacute;rt&eacute;kelő</a> biztosan a csal&aacute;dv&eacute;delmi akci&oacute;tervnek elnevezett d&ouml;nt&eacute;sek bejelent&eacute;s&eacute;ről lesz eml&eacute;kezetes. Nem mell&eacute;kes azonban, hogy milyen k&ouml;r&uuml;lm&eacute;nyek k&ouml;z&ouml;tt rendezt&eacute;k ezt az &eacute;v&eacute;rt&eacute;kelőt.</p><p style="text-align: justify;">Balog Zolt&aacute;n az Orb&aacute;nt felvezető besz&eacute;d&eacute;ben azt mondta, hogy &quot;soha ennyien nem akartak &eacute;v&eacute;rt&eacute;kelőre bejutni&quot;, &aacute;m ezt k&iacute;v&uuml;lről nem hagyt&aacute;k meg&iacute;t&eacute;lni. M&iacute;g kor&aacute;bban a megh&iacute;vottak előszeretettel nyilatkoztak a v&aacute;rakoz&aacute;saikr&oacute;l, sz&iacute;vesen dics&eacute;rt&eacute;k Orb&aacute;n Viktor korm&aacute;nyz&aacute;s&aacute;t az ott gy&uuml;lekező &uacute;js&aacute;g&iacute;r&oacute;knak, most <a data-recommendation="bekezdes_utan" data-recommendation-id="4567146" data-recommendation-preview='{"og:title":"Fekete kordonnal zárták el a Várkert Bazárt az évértékel\u0151 miatt","og:description":"Így azt sem lehet látni, kik érkeznek Orbán Viktor évértékel\u0151jére.","og:image":"\/\/kep.cdn.indexvas.hu\/1\/0\/2650\/26507\/265075\/26507586_2032130_87890adfaaffe5c4e48fb7c2fecef7bf_wm.jpg"}' href="https://index.hu/belfold/2019/02/10/fekete_kordon_orban_evertekelo_varkert_bazar/" target="_self" title="Fekete kordonnal zárták el a Várkert Bazárt az évértékelő miatt">fekete lepellel leter&iacute;tett kordonokkal</a> takart&aacute;k el az &eacute;rkező vend&eacute;gsereget. A dolog nem v&eacute;letlen: az ellenz&eacute;k ugyanis az MSZP-től a DK-n &eacute;s az LMP-n &aacute;t a Jobbikig k&ouml;z&ouml;s t&uuml;ntet&eacute;st hirdetett. A szervezők a jelek szerint mindenk&eacute;pp meg akartak előzni b&aacute;rmilyen atrocit&aacute;st, amely elterelhetn&eacute; a f&oacute;kuszt a besz&eacute;d tartalm&aacute;r&oacute;l</p><p style="text-align: justify;">The original 50 cm statuette of the <em><strong>Little Princess</strong></em> (Kiskir&aacute;lyl&aacute;ny)&nbsp;<strong>statue</strong> sitting on the railings of the Danube promenade in&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Budapest" title="Budapest">Budapest</a>,&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hungary" title="Hungary">Hungary</a> was created by&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%C3%A1szl%C3%B3_Marton_(sculptor)" title="László Marton (sculptor)">L&aacute;szl&oacute; Marton</a> (1925&ndash;2008)&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Munk%C3%A1csy_Prize&action=edit&redlink=1" title="Munkácsy Prize (page does not exist)">Munk&aacute;csy</a>- and&nbsp;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kossuth_Prize" title="Kossuth Prize">Kossuth Prize</a>-winning sculptor in 1972.</p><p style="text-align: justify;">The artist was inspired by his eldest daughter born from his first marriage. She often played in the Tab&aacute;n wearing a princess costume and a crown made out of newspaper by her father, and at home as well, pretending her bathrobes were a mantle. This image prompted her father, the artist in the creation of this little statue.</p><p style="text-align: justify;">L&aacute;szl&oacute; Marton writes: &quot;<em>&Eacute;vike</em> born from my first marriage, at the age of 5, was playing in a little princess costume in the Tab&aacute;n playground. When I saw it, I immediately had the subject matter. Titled &quot;Little Princess&quot; I sculpted it as well. It was placed in an elegant location on the Danube promenade. Became a symbol of Budapest.</p>